  "title": "What_s my other option",
  "movie": "",
  "duration_sec": 699.51,
  "audio_url": "https://rtyzdyyfahddqshgyjvn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/gmp-audio/2021-10-20_screen_english.mp3",
  "script": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 1.2,
      "text": "Screen English"
    },
    {
      "start": 1.2,
      "end": 22.36,
      "text": "비영화 구독 서비스 Screen English Time"
    },
    {
      "start": 22.36,
      "end": 25.62,
      "text": "10월에 함께하고 있는 영화는 After the Wedding"
    },
    {
      "start": 25.62,
      "end": 27.8,
      "text": "After Wedding in New York"
    },
    {
      "start": 27.8,
      "end": 33.24,
      "text": "A wonderful movie that stars Julianne Moore, Michelle Williams, Billy Crudup, and Abby Quinn"
    },
    {
      "start": 33.24,
      "end": 35.4,
      "text": "와우 오셨어요 오셨어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 35.4,
      "end": 36.3,
      "text": "I'm here"
    },
    {
      "start": 36.3,
      "end": 37.08,
      "text": "Hey there"
    },
    {
      "start": 37.08,
      "end": 38.74,
      "text": "네 다보기님께서"
    },
    {
      "start": 38.74,
      "end": 40.3,
      "text": "크리스쌤 하이"
    },
    {
      "start": 40.3,
      "end": 41.14,
      "text": "우승우승"
    },
    {
      "start": 41.14,
      "end": 42.02,
      "text": "Hello"
    },
    {
      "start": 42.02,
      "end": 44.82,
      "text": "네 이렇게 기쁘게 인사 건네주셨고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 45.66,
      "end": 50.92,
      "text": "이 After Wedding in New York 이라는 제목 하에 우리가 내용을 살펴보고 있잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 51.18,
      "end": 52.88,
      "text": "Yeah things are getting really really serious."
    },
    {
      "start": 53.1,
      "end": 58.24,
      "text": "어 근데 일단 Wedding in New York 이거 자체만 한번 상상을 해보면"
    },
    {
      "start": 58.24,
      "end": 59.66,
      "text": "That sounds like a good event."
    },
    {
      "start": 59.72,
      "end": 62.26,
      "text": "Yeah 아주 로맨틱하고 wonderful 할 것 같습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 62.5,
      "end": 63.34,
      "text": "It's an outdoor wedding"
    },
    {
      "start": 63.34,
      "end": 64.04,
      "text": "Oh 맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 64.22,
      "end": 66.94,
      "text": "At a private home in the front yard"
    },
    {
      "start": 66.94,
      "end": 70.1,
      "text": "네 저의 상상을 좀 더 구체화 시켜주시니까 너무 행복해지네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 70.16,
      "end": 71.0,
      "text": "Beautiful flowers"
    },
    {
      "start": 71.0,
      "end": 71.44,
      "text": "Wow"
    },
    {
      "start": 71.44,
      "end": 72.94,
      "text": "Beautiful green lawn"
    },
    {
      "start": 72.94,
      "end": 74.14,
      "text": "와 너무 아름다워요."
    },
    {
      "start": 74.34,
      "end": 75.46,
      "text": "Close friends and family"
    },
    {
      "start": 75.46,
      "end": 77.9,
      "text": "네 아마 그렇게 이 테레사도"
    },
    {
      "start": 77.9,
      "end": 79.82,
      "text": "Had a wedding in New York 했었을 겁니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 80.36,
      "end": 80.82,
      "text": "She did"
    },
    {
      "start": 80.82,
      "end": 81.3,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 81.3,
      "end": 83.38,
      "text": "근데 만약에 이제"
    },
    {
      "start": 83.38,
      "end": 87.94,
      "text": "Would have been so nice if the marriage was continuously romantic forever"
    },
    {
      "start": 87.94,
      "end": 90.18,
      "text": "Oh wouldn't that be nice?"
    },
    {
      "start": 90.32,
      "end": 92.58,
      "text": "Wouldn't it be nice for everybody"
    },
    {
      "start": 92.58,
      "end": 94.54,
      "text": "If the romance lasted"
    },
    {
      "start": 94.54,
      "end": 95.04,
      "text": "Uh-huh"
    },
    {
      "start": 95.04,
      "end": 97.08,
      "text": "하지만 그렇게 되기가 좀 쉽지는 않죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 97.2,
      "end": 97.46,
      "text": "그쵸?"
    },
    {
      "start": 97.66,
      "end": 98.02,
      "text": "Sure"
    },
    {
      "start": 98.02,
      "end": 98.8,
      "text": "Hamilton"
    },
    {
      "start": 98.8,
      "end": 102.26,
      "text": "Now we happen to focus on the story about Teresa"
    },
    {
      "start": 102.26,
      "end": 103.56,
      "text": "Yeah Teresa"
    },
    {
      "start": 103.56,
      "end": 105.18,
      "text": "So she was"
    },
    {
      "start": 105.18,
      "end": 106.5,
      "text": "This is kind of a spoiler"
    },
    {
      "start": 106.5,
      "end": 108.14,
      "text": "But we mentioned it yesterday"
    },
    {
      "start": 108.14,
      "end": 108.7,
      "text": "Wow"
    },
    {
      "start": 108.7,
      "end": 109.72,
      "text": "This is the time"
    },
    {
      "start": 109.72,
      "end": 111.2,
      "text": "This is another big twist"
    },
    {
      "start": 111.2,
      "end": 112.56,
      "text": "The time is to reveal"
    },
    {
      "start": 112.56,
      "end": 113.16,
      "text": "Here is here"
    },
    {
      "start": 113.16,
      "end": 113.36,
      "text": "Okay"
    },
    {
      "start": 113.36,
      "end": 115.16,
      "text": "To reveal another big twist"
    },
    {
      "start": 115.16,
      "end": 115.48,
      "text": "Uh-huh"
    },
    {
      "start": 115.48,
      "end": 118.04,
      "text": "So she has an illness"
    },
    {
      "start": 118.04,
      "end": 120.28,
      "text": "Not a light illness"
    },
    {
      "start": 120.28,
      "end": 121.78,
      "text": "It's a terminal illness"
    },
    {
      "start": 121.78,
      "end": 124.18,
      "text": "Oh you mean incurable disease"
    },
    {
      "start": 124.18,
      "end": 124.82,
      "text": "Incurable"
    },
    {
      "start": 124.82,
      "end": 125.3,
      "text": "Oh"
    },
    {
      "start": 125.3,
      "end": 128.08,
      "text": "So she doesn't have much longer to live"
    },
    {
      "start": 128.08,
      "end": 128.62,
      "text": "Uh-oh"
    },
    {
      "start": 128.62,
      "end": 129.46,
      "text": "Terminally ill"
    },
    {
      "start": 129.46,
      "end": 132.22,
      "text": "And she has been hiding this from all her family"
    },
    {
      "start": 132.22,
      "end": 132.82,
      "text": "So sad"
    },
    {
      "start": 132.82,
      "end": 133.76,
      "text": "Nobody knows"
    },
    {
      "start": 133.76,
      "end": 136.6,
      "text": "She doesn't want to trouble them with her illness"
    },
    {
      "start": 136.6,
      "end": 138.46,
      "text": "She hides her medicine"
    },
    {
      "start": 138.46,
      "end": 139.24,
      "text": "Uh-huh"
    },
    {
      "start": 139.24,
      "end": 140.42,
      "text": "And she locks it away"
    },
    {
      "start": 140.42,
      "end": 140.84,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 140.84,
      "end": 142.26,
      "text": "It felt for her so much"
    },
    {
      "start": 142.26,
      "end": 142.64,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 142.64,
      "end": 144.16,
      "text": "So when we find this out"
    },
    {
      "start": 144.16,
      "end": 145.32,
      "text": "We do feel for her"
    },
    {
      "start": 145.32,
      "end": 147.18,
      "text": "We understand her situation"
    },
    {
      "start": 147.18,
      "end": 150.96,
      "text": "And why she is doing all these seemingly crazy things"
    },
    {
      "start": 150.96,
      "end": 152.06,
      "text": "She has a reason"
    },
    {
      "start": 152.06,
      "end": 152.48,
      "text": "네"
    },
    {
      "start": 152.48,
      "end": 155.7,
      "text": "치료할 수 없는 불치병으로 인해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 155.7,
      "end": 159.12,
      "text": "정말 시안부 선고를 받은 상황이었다라는 거죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 159.12,
      "end": 162.56,
      "text": "그래서 이제 얼마 남지 않은 삶을 두고"
    },
    {
      "start": 162.56,
      "end": 164.16,
      "text": "정리도 하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 164.16,
      "end": 168.54,
      "text": "그러면서 이제 이자벨을 찾은 이유가 다 있었다라는 걸 이해하게 됩니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 168.54,
      "end": 170.32,
      "text": "그나저나 정말"
    },
    {
      "start": 170.32,
      "end": 172.78,
      "text": "I can't imagine how hard it is"
    },
    {
      "start": 172.78,
      "end": 173.36,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 173.36,
      "end": 176.56,
      "text": "나의 입장이라면 얼마나 이게 힘들까"
    },
    {
      "start": 176.56,
      "end": 177.18,
      "text": "If it were you"
    },
    {
      "start": 177.18,
      "end": 179.1,
      "text": "상상도 못하겠어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 179.1,
      "end": 181.28,
      "text": "She has to call her daughters"
    },
    {
      "start": 181.28,
      "end": 183.6,
      "text": "The girl she raised as a daughter"
    },
    {
      "start": 183.6,
      "end": 186.18,
      "text": "Call her real mom from India"
    },
    {
      "start": 186.18,
      "end": 187.9,
      "text": "Give her money"
    },
    {
      "start": 187.9,
      "end": 188.98,
      "text": "Okay"
    },
    {
      "start": 188.98,
      "end": 192.36,
      "text": "Now we understand why she wants her to stay in New York"
    },
    {
      "start": 192.36,
      "end": 195.58,
      "text": "I think she's trying to arrange all her affairs"
    },
    {
      "start": 195.58,
      "end": 198.2,
      "text": "For after she passes away"
    },
    {
      "start": 198.2,
      "end": 203.18,
      "text": "음 사실 뭐 누군가에게 가족까지 포함해가지고"
    },
    {
      "start": 203.18,
      "end": 206.18,
      "text": "Give everything 한다라는 거 쉽지 않은 일이잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 206.18,
      "end": 206.6,
      "text": "Sure"
    },
    {
      "start": 206.6,
      "end": 208.69,
      "text": "와 참 공감이 많이 됩니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 208.69,
      "end": 212.01,
      "text": "일단은 오늘 장면 먼저 듣고 오겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 212.01,
      "end": 214.15,
      "text": "I hate fighting with you"
    },
    {
      "start": 214.15,
      "end": 216.83,
      "text": "You think you're ever going to forgive me?"
    },
    {
      "start": 217.73,
      "end": 218.75,
      "text": "That's my other option"
    },
    {
      "start": 218.75,
      "end": 220.65,
      "text": "But I want to know everything"
    },
    {
      "start": 220.65,
      "end": 223.3,
      "text": "When you give a child up for adoption"
    },
    {
      "start": 223.3,
      "end": 225.7,
      "text": "You've got 30 days to change your mind"
    },
    {
      "start": 225.7,
      "end": 227.78,
      "text": "A grace period"
    },
    {
      "start": 227.78,
      "end": 230.8,
      "text": "How long did it take you to decide to come get me?"
    },
    {
      "start": 231.32,
      "end": 232.12,
      "text": "29 days"
    },
    {
      "start": 232.12,
      "end": 234.26,
      "text": "Actually"
    },
    {
      "start": 234.26,
      "end": 236.0,
      "text": "이 장면을 들으면서"
    },
    {
      "start": 236.0,
      "end": 237.32,
      "text": "I thought of a saying that"
    },
    {
      "start": 237.32,
      "end": 240.02,
      "text": "Blood is thicker than water"
    },
    {
      "start": 240.02,
      "end": 241.02,
      "text": "That's a good saying"
    },
    {
      "start": 241.02,
      "end": 244.08,
      "text": "피는 물보다 진하다라는 말이 생각이 났어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 244.08,
      "end": 245.64,
      "text": "Blood is thicker than water"
    },
    {
      "start": 245.64,
      "end": 246.06,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 246.06,
      "end": 246.66,
      "text": "왜냐하면"
    },
    {
      "start": 246.66,
      "end": 248.7,
      "text": "She was so angry a lot"
    },
    {
      "start": 248.7,
      "end": 249.2,
      "text": "그죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 249.36,
      "end": 249.8,
      "text": "Furious"
    },
    {
      "start": 249.8,
      "end": 251.34,
      "text": "왜냐하면 아빠한테 약간"
    },
    {
      "start": 251.34,
      "end": 254.32,
      "text": "Betrayed 당했다라고 생각을 했었을 테니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 254.32,
      "end": 255.96,
      "text": "화가 많이 났었을 거란 말이죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 255.96,
      "end": 257.7,
      "text": "I would be angry at first too"
    },
    {
      "start": 257.7,
      "end": 259.16,
      "text": "Her dad told her"
    },
    {
      "start": 259.16,
      "end": 260.26,
      "text": "Her mom died"
    },
    {
      "start": 260.26,
      "end": 262.06,
      "text": "While her mom is alive"
    },
    {
      "start": 262.06,
      "end": 262.92,
      "text": "She's healthy"
    },
    {
      "start": 262.92,
      "end": 264.18,
      "text": "She's living in India"
    },
    {
      "start": 264.18,
      "end": 266.4,
      "text": "But he didn't say anything about them"
    },
    {
      "start": 266.4,
      "end": 268.58,
      "text": "그래서 엄청 화가 나서"
    },
    {
      "start": 268.58,
      "end": 272.12,
      "text": "다시는 용서하지 않을 것 같아 보였지만"
    },
    {
      "start": 272.12,
      "end": 273.46,
      "text": "그리고 나서"
    },
    {
      "start": 273.46,
      "end": 277.0,
      "text": "She didn't try to make up with him again"
    },
    {
      "start": 277.0,
      "end": 277.4,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 277.4,
      "end": 278.88,
      "text": "So she realizes"
    },
    {
      "start": 278.88,
      "end": 280.24,
      "text": "This is her dad"
    },
    {
      "start": 280.24,
      "end": 281.8,
      "text": "No matter what he did"
    },
    {
      "start": 281.8,
      "end": 282.96,
      "text": "She loves her dad"
    },
    {
      "start": 282.96,
      "end": 284.96,
      "text": "And she wants to be close to him"
    },
    {
      "start": 284.96,
      "end": 286.6,
      "text": "So she has no choice"
    },
    {
      "start": 286.6,
      "end": 288.36,
      "text": "But to forgive him"
    },
    {
      "start": 288.36,
      "end": 289.68,
      "text": "And I also understand"
    },
    {
      "start": 289.68,
      "end": 291.26,
      "text": "He wanted to protect his daughter"
    },
    {
      "start": 291.26,
      "end": 291.96,
      "text": "That's right"
    },
    {
      "start": 291.96,
      "end": 294.06,
      "text": "Because he was afraid she would be hurt"
    },
    {
      "start": 294.06,
      "end": 296.96,
      "text": "If she found out that her mom just left"
    },
    {
      "start": 296.96,
      "end": 298.78,
      "text": "And gave her up for adoption"
    },
    {
      "start": 298.78,
      "end": 301.18,
      "text": "But I don't know"
    },
    {
      "start": 301.18,
      "end": 303.56,
      "text": "When should he tell her"
    },
    {
      "start": 303.56,
      "end": 305.46,
      "text": "That her mom is alive?"
    },
    {
      "start": 306.32,
      "end": 307.94,
      "text": "처음부터 죽었던 얘기"
    },
    {
      "start": 307.94,
      "end": 309.1,
      "text": "안 했으면 되는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 309.1,
      "end": 309.48,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 309.48,
      "end": 310.46,
      "text": "아무튼"
    },
    {
      "start": 310.46,
      "end": 312.7,
      "text": "자 주요 표현들 점검을 해볼까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 313.28,
      "end": 314.12,
      "text": "Other option"
    },
    {
      "start": 314.12,
      "end": 315.42,
      "text": "Other option"
    },
    {
      "start": 315.42,
      "end": 316.86,
      "text": "다른 선택지"
    },
    {
      "start": 316.86,
      "end": 318.26,
      "text": "혹은 다른 방법"
    },
    {
      "start": 318.26,
      "end": 319.76,
      "text": "이라고 해석하시면 됐네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 319.76,
      "end": 321.34,
      "text": "We have no other option"
    },
    {
      "start": 321.34,
      "end": 323.7,
      "text": "Or what is the other option?"
    },
    {
      "start": 324.06,
      "end": 325.94,
      "text": "다른 선택지가 뭐가 있을까?"
    },
    {
      "start": 326.38,
      "end": 327.8,
      "text": "다른 방법은 없을까?"
    },
    {
      "start": 328.0,
      "end": 328.62,
      "text": "라고 할 때"
    },
    {
      "start": 328.62,
      "end": 329.98,
      "text": "쓸 수가 있겠네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 329.98,
      "end": 331.52,
      "text": "That's what I'm thinking about right now"
    },
    {
      "start": 331.52,
      "end": 333.08,
      "text": "If I were her dad"
    },
    {
      "start": 333.08,
      "end": 334.62,
      "text": "What is the other option?"
    },
    {
      "start": 334.8,
      "end": 336.86,
      "text": "What should I do in this situation?"
    },
    {
      "start": 337.08,
      "end": 338.2,
      "text": "In his shoes?"
    },
    {
      "start": 339.96,
      "end": 341.68,
      "text": "Give a child up for adoption"
    },
    {
      "start": 341.68,
      "end": 343.68,
      "text": "Give a child up for adoption"
    },
    {
      "start": 343.68,
      "end": 346.14,
      "text": "아이를 입양 보내다"
    },
    {
      "start": 346.14,
      "end": 347.0,
      "text": "라는 표현입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 347.0,
      "end": 348.88,
      "text": "A grace period"
    },
    {
      "start": 348.88,
      "end": 350.92,
      "text": "A grace period"
    },
    {
      "start": 350.92,
      "end": 352.4,
      "text": "라는 게 소위"
    },
    {
      "start": 352.4,
      "end": 353.88,
      "text": "유예 기간"
    },
    {
      "start": 353.88,
      "end": 355.28,
      "text": "이라는 명칭입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 355.28,
      "end": 357.28,
      "text": "Yeah, this has to do with the adoption"
    },
    {
      "start": 357.28,
      "end": 357.86,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 357.86,
      "end": 359.22,
      "text": "There was a grace period"
    },
    {
      "start": 359.22,
      "end": 360.68,
      "text": "And that happens to be"
    },
    {
      "start": 360.68,
      "end": 362.0,
      "text": "his daughter's name"
    },
    {
      "start": 362.0,
      "end": 363.38,
      "text": "His daughter's name is Grace"
    },
    {
      "start": 363.38,
      "end": 365.54,
      "text": "이게 what a coincidence인지"
    },
    {
      "start": 365.54,
      "end": 366.44,
      "text": "아니면 뭔가"
    },
    {
      "start": 366.44,
      "end": 368.04,
      "text": "He had a grace period"
    },
    {
      "start": 368.04,
      "end": 369.6,
      "text": "for 30 days"
    },
    {
      "start": 369.6,
      "end": 370.46,
      "text": "as I remember"
    },
    {
      "start": 370.46,
      "end": 371.64,
      "text": "Yeah, after you decide"
    },
    {
      "start": 371.64,
      "end": 372.96,
      "text": "to give your kid up for adoption"
    },
    {
      "start": 372.96,
      "end": 374.64,
      "text": "you can change your mind"
    },
    {
      "start": 374.64,
      "end": 376.78,
      "text": "within 30 days"
    },
    {
      "start": 376.78,
      "end": 377.1,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 377.1,
      "end": 378.06,
      "text": "That's the grace period"
    },
    {
      "start": 378.06,
      "end": 379.78,
      "text": "그래서 he named his daughter"
    },
    {
      "start": 379.78,
      "end": 380.4,
      "text": "Grace?"
    },
    {
      "start": 380.96,
      "end": 381.46,
      "text": "Maybe"
    },
    {
      "start": 381.46,
      "end": 382.16,
      "text": "Maybe"
    },
    {
      "start": 382.16,
      "end": 383.58,
      "text": "It's a coincidence"
    },
    {
      "start": 383.58,
      "end": 383.8,
      "text": "I'm not sure"
    },
    {
      "start": 383.8,
      "end": 386.08,
      "text": "Anyway, it's a very fitting name"
    },
    {
      "start": 386.08,
      "end": 386.42,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 386.42,
      "end": 388.82,
      "text": "참 우연인지 아닌지는 모르겠지만"
    },
    {
      "start": 388.82,
      "end": 389.44,
      "text": "아무튼"
    },
    {
      "start": 389.44,
      "end": 390.56,
      "text": "a grace period"
    },
    {
      "start": 390.56,
      "end": 392.56,
      "text": "유예 기간이라는 의미였고"
    },
    {
      "start": 392.56,
      "end": 394.12,
      "text": "이 딸의 이름도"
    },
    {
      "start": 394.12,
      "end": 395.1,
      "text": "Grace였다"
    },
    {
      "start": 395.1,
      "end": 395.88,
      "text": "하는 것까지"
    },
    {
      "start": 395.88,
      "end": 396.68,
      "text": "알려드립니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 396.68,
      "end": 397.38,
      "text": "Perfect name"
    },
    {
      "start": 397.38,
      "end": 397.68,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 397.68,
      "end": 398.7,
      "text": "자, 이 장면"
    },
    {
      "start": 398.7,
      "end": 399.58,
      "text": "다시 한번 들어볼게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 399.58,
      "end": 401.7,
      "text": "I hate fighting with you"
    },
    {
      "start": 401.7,
      "end": 404.36,
      "text": "You think you're ever going to forgive me?"
    },
    {
      "start": 405.3,
      "end": 406.3,
      "text": "That's my other option"
    },
    {
      "start": 406.3,
      "end": 408.2,
      "text": "But I want to know everything"
    },
    {
      "start": 408.2,
      "end": 410.84,
      "text": "When you give a child up for adoption"
    },
    {
      "start": 410.84,
      "end": 412.47,
      "text": "you've got 30 days"
    },
    {
      "start": 412.47,
      "end": 413.27,
      "text": "to change your mind"
    },
    {
      "start": 413.27,
      "end": 415.37,
      "text": "A grace period"
    },
    {
      "start": 415.37,
      "end": 417.37,
      "text": "How long did it take you"
    },
    {
      "start": 417.37,
      "end": 418.33,
      "text": "to decide to come get me?"
    },
    {
      "start": 418.85,
      "end": 419.69,
      "text": "29 days"
    },
    {
      "start": 419.69,
      "end": 421.17,
      "text": "와우"
    },
    {
      "start": 421.17,
      "end": 423.01,
      "text": "29일간"
    },
    {
      "start": 423.01,
      "end": 424.97,
      "text": "얼마나 많은 고민과"
    },
    {
      "start": 424.97,
      "end": 426.51,
      "text": "갈등을 했을지"
    },
    {
      "start": 426.51,
      "end": 427.45,
      "text": "가슴이 굉장히"
    },
    {
      "start": 427.45,
      "end": 428.35,
      "text": "먹먹해졌어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 428.35,
      "end": 428.65,
      "text": "저는"
    },
    {
      "start": 428.65,
      "end": 429.49,
      "text": "Yeah, me too"
    },
    {
      "start": 429.49,
      "end": 431.95,
      "text": "He waited until the very last day"
    },
    {
      "start": 431.95,
      "end": 432.63,
      "text": "That's right"
    },
    {
      "start": 432.63,
      "end": 433.77,
      "text": "To take her back"
    },
    {
      "start": 433.77,
      "end": 434.97,
      "text": "and raise her"
    },
    {
      "start": 434.97,
      "end": 436.15,
      "text": "as his own daughter"
    },
    {
      "start": 436.15,
      "end": 438.57,
      "text": "자, Grace가 먼저"
    },
    {
      "start": 438.57,
      "end": 439.61,
      "text": "뭐라고 했죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 440.58,
      "end": 441.96,
      "text": "I hate fighting with you"
    },
    {
      "start": 441.96,
      "end": 443.92,
      "text": "아빠랑 싸우는 거"
    },
    {
      "start": 443.92,
      "end": 444.4,
      "text": "hate"
    },
    {
      "start": 444.4,
      "end": 445.06,
      "text": "싫어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 445.06,
      "end": 446.48,
      "text": "I hate fighting with you"
    },
    {
      "start": 446.48,
      "end": 447.56,
      "text": "Oh, I would feel so good"
    },
    {
      "start": 447.56,
      "end": 448.34,
      "text": "as a dad"
    },
    {
      "start": 448.34,
      "end": 450.26,
      "text": "when she comes up to me"
    },
    {
      "start": 450.26,
      "end": 451.26,
      "text": "after fighting"
    },
    {
      "start": 451.26,
      "end": 452.92,
      "text": "I hate fighting with you, dad"
    },
    {
      "start": 452.92,
      "end": 454.8,
      "text": "Oh, 딸이 아빠한테"
    },
    {
      "start": 454.8,
      "end": 456.88,
      "text": "아빠, 나는 아빠랑 싸우는 거 싫어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 456.88,
      "end": 457.64,
      "text": "이렇게 이야기를 하면"
    },
    {
      "start": 457.64,
      "end": 459.24,
      "text": "얼마나 더 사랑스러워 보일까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 459.64,
      "end": 460.76,
      "text": "Let's make up"
    },
    {
      "start": 460.76,
      "end": 462.22,
      "text": "우리 화해해요"
    },
    {
      "start": 462.22,
      "end": 463.76,
      "text": "If it's your wife or husband"
    },
    {
      "start": 463.76,
      "end": 465.18,
      "text": "그냥 가만히 있어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 465.18,
      "end": 466.36,
      "text": "그냥 가만히 있어요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 467.18,
      "end": 468.76,
      "text": "It's not so amazing"
    },
    {
      "start": 468.76,
      "end": 469.64,
      "text": "아, 그래요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 469.82,
      "end": 471.44,
      "text": "역시 딸과 다르네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 471.44,
      "end": 472.24,
      "text": "존재 자체가"
    },
    {
      "start": 472.24,
      "end": 473.52,
      "text": "물론 양적 좋지만"
    },
    {
      "start": 473.52,
      "end": 475.18,
      "text": "딸 더 달라요"
    },
    {
      "start": 475.18,
      "end": 476.92,
      "text": "그래서 피는 물보다 진하다라는"
    },
    {
      "start": 476.92,
      "end": 478.36,
      "text": "속담이 딱이네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 478.36,
      "end": 478.82,
      "text": "Yes"
    },
    {
      "start": 478.82,
      "end": 480.4,
      "text": "Especially father, daughter"
    },
    {
      "start": 480.4,
      "end": 481.36,
      "text": "mother, daughter"
    },
    {
      "start": 481.36,
      "end": 483.32,
      "text": "부모, 자식"
    },
    {
      "start": 483.32,
      "end": 483.94,
      "text": "그 피"
    },
    {
      "start": 483.94,
      "end": 484.38,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 484.38,
      "end": 484.9,
      "text": "그 피"
    },
    {
      "start": 484.9,
      "end": 486.1,
      "text": "is very, very 진해"
    },
    {
      "start": 486.1,
      "end": 486.4,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 486.4,
      "end": 489.26,
      "text": "You think you're ever gonna forgive me?"
    },
    {
      "start": 489.76,
      "end": 491.32,
      "text": "아빠가 이렇게 대답했습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 491.32,
      "end": 493.64,
      "text": "You think you're ever gonna forgive me?"
    },
    {
      "start": 494.36,
      "end": 496.96,
      "text": "나를 용서할 수 있겠니?"
    },
    {
      "start": 497.22,
      "end": 497.74,
      "text": "라는 겁니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 497.74,
      "end": 499.7,
      "text": "What's my other option?"
    },
    {
      "start": 500.5,
      "end": 502.0,
      "text": "뭐, 또 다른 선택지가 있어요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 502.26,
      "end": 503.34,
      "text": "라는 질문이잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 503.34,
      "end": 505.66,
      "text": "뭐, 화해할 수밖에 없잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 505.66,
      "end": 506.74,
      "text": "라는 뉘앙스입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 506.74,
      "end": 507.96,
      "text": "What's my other option?"
    },
    {
      "start": 508.44,
      "end": 509.36,
      "text": "That's good"
    },
    {
      "start": 509.36,
      "end": 511.1,
      "text": "She can't just leave her dad"
    },
    {
      "start": 511.1,
      "end": 512.71,
      "text": "But"
    },
    {
      "start": 512.71,
      "end": 514.39,
      "text": "Oh, condition-y so"
    },
    {
      "start": 514.39,
      "end": 514.71,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 514.71,
      "end": 515.59,
      "text": "I have a condition"
    },
    {
      "start": 515.59,
      "end": 515.89,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 515.89,
      "end": 518.05,
      "text": "I wanna know everything"
    },
    {
      "start": 518.05,
      "end": 519.37,
      "text": "화해를 할 테니"
    },
    {
      "start": 519.37,
      "end": 521.29,
      "text": "조건을 이야기하는 거네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 521.29,
      "end": 522.89,
      "text": "But I wanna know everything"
    },
    {
      "start": 522.89,
      "end": 524.81,
      "text": "하지만 대신에"
    },
    {
      "start": 524.81,
      "end": 526.79,
      "text": "나는 모든 거를 다 알기를 원해요"
    },
    {
      "start": 526.79,
      "end": 527.47,
      "text": "라는 거니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 527.47,
      "end": 529.27,
      "text": "That's a very understandable condition"
    },
    {
      "start": 529.27,
      "end": 529.69,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 529.69,
      "end": 532.07,
      "text": "솔직하게 모든 일을 다 말해주세요"
    },
    {
      "start": 532.07,
      "end": 533.05,
      "text": "라는 의미가 되겠죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 533.05,
      "end": 534.43,
      "text": "Okay, now her dad"
    },
    {
      "start": 534.43,
      "end": 535.81,
      "text": "is gonna tell her everything"
    },
    {
      "start": 535.81,
      "end": 538.71,
      "text": "When you give a child up for adoption"
    },
    {
      "start": 538.71,
      "end": 540.45,
      "text": "you've got 30 days"
    },
    {
      "start": 540.45,
      "end": 541.53,
      "text": "to change your mind"
    },
    {
      "start": 541.53,
      "end": 544.51,
      "text": "When you give a child up for adoption"
    },
    {
      "start": 544.51,
      "end": 547.13,
      "text": "아이를 입양 보낼 때"
    },
    {
      "start": 547.13,
      "end": 549.37,
      "text": "you've got 30 days"
    },
    {
      "start": 549.37,
      "end": 551.13,
      "text": "to change your mind"
    },
    {
      "start": 551.13,
      "end": 551.87,
      "text": "라고 했습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 551.87,
      "end": 554.69,
      "text": "너의 마음을 바꿀 수 있는"
    },
    {
      "start": 554.69,
      "end": 556.71,
      "text": "30일이 주어진다"
    },
    {
      "start": 556.71,
      "end": 557.15,
      "text": "라는 거예요"
    },
    {
      "start": 557.15,
      "end": 559.01,
      "text": "30일 안에 마음을 바꿀 수 있어"
    },
    {
      "start": 559.01,
      "end": 560.19,
      "text": "I didn't know this"
    },
    {
      "start": 560.19,
      "end": 560.97,
      "text": "Me neither"
    },
    {
      "start": 560.97,
      "end": 561.87,
      "text": "But this makes sense"
    },
    {
      "start": 561.87,
      "end": 562.35,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 562.35,
      "end": 563.83,
      "text": "It's a big decision"
    },
    {
      "start": 563.83,
      "end": 565.75,
      "text": "되게 좋은 기간인 것 같아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 565.75,
      "end": 566.31,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 566.31,
      "end": 567.51,
      "text": "So I guess they keep the baby"
    },
    {
      "start": 567.51,
      "end": 568.19,
      "text": "in a hospital"
    },
    {
      "start": 568.19,
      "end": 569.39,
      "text": "or orphanage"
    },
    {
      "start": 569.39,
      "end": 570.45,
      "text": "for 30 days"
    },
    {
      "start": 570.45,
      "end": 572.15,
      "text": "until they decide"
    },
    {
      "start": 572.15,
      "end": 573.73,
      "text": "make the final decision"
    },
    {
      "start": 573.73,
      "end": 576.07,
      "text": "A grace period"
    },
    {
      "start": 576.07,
      "end": 576.73,
      "text": "바로 그게"
    },
    {
      "start": 576.73,
      "end": 578.01,
      "text": "A grace period"
    },
    {
      "start": 578.01,
      "end": 579.21,
      "text": "라는 거라는 겁니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 579.21,
      "end": 580.89,
      "text": "유예 기간이지"
    },
    {
      "start": 580.89,
      "end": 581.65,
      "text": "라고 하면서"
    },
    {
      "start": 581.65,
      "end": 582.81,
      "text": "이 아빠가요"
    },
    {
      "start": 582.81,
      "end": 584.43,
      "text": "목소리가 울먹 울먹 했어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 584.43,
      "end": 585.87,
      "text": "특히 period"
    },
    {
      "start": 585.87,
      "end": 586.87,
      "text": "라고 이야기할 때"
    },
    {
      "start": 586.87,
      "end": 587.87,
      "text": "She's a grace"
    },
    {
      "start": 587.87,
      "end": 589.27,
      "text": "and he starts crying"
    },
    {
      "start": 589.27,
      "end": 590.11,
      "text": "period"
    },
    {
      "start": 590.11,
      "end": 590.81,
      "text": "그쵸"
    },
    {
      "start": 590.81,
      "end": 591.67,
      "text": "A grace period"
    },
    {
      "start": 591.67,
      "end": 591.95,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 591.95,
      "end": 593.27,
      "text": "You can feel his emotion"
    },
    {
      "start": 593.27,
      "end": 596.1,
      "text": "How long did it take you"
    },
    {
      "start": 596.1,
      "end": 597.7,
      "text": "to decide to come get me?"
    },
    {
      "start": 598.12,
      "end": 599.82,
      "text": "아주 똑똑하게 질문을 하네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 599.82,
      "end": 600.58,
      "text": "Very idiot"
    },
    {
      "start": 600.58,
      "end": 602.36,
      "text": "Very good question"
    },
    {
      "start": 602.36,
      "end": 604.76,
      "text": "How long did it take you"
    },
    {
      "start": 604.76,
      "end": 605.62,
      "text": "to decide"
    },
    {
      "start": 605.62,
      "end": 607.06,
      "text": "to come get me?"
    },
    {
      "start": 607.16,
      "end": 607.62,
      "text": "라고 했습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 607.62,
      "end": 608.76,
      "text": "잘 들리셨죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 609.26,
      "end": 610.78,
      "text": "얼마나 오래 걸렸어요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 610.78,
      "end": 612.12,
      "text": "결정하는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 612.12,
      "end": 614.22,
      "text": "나를 데리러 오려고"
    },
    {
      "start": 614.22,
      "end": 614.86,
      "text": "결정하는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 614.86,
      "end": 616.24,
      "text": "얼마나 오래 걸렸어요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 616.44,
      "end": 616.94,
      "text": "라는 겁니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 616.94,
      "end": 617.68,
      "text": "What did you think"
    },
    {
      "start": 617.68,
      "end": 618.42,
      "text": "he was going to say?"
    },
    {
      "start": 618.5,
      "end": 619.84,
      "text": "I thought he was going to say"
    },
    {
      "start": 619.84,
      "end": 621.34,
      "text": "like one hour"
    },
    {
      "start": 621.34,
      "end": 622.5,
      "text": "I went right back"
    },
    {
      "start": 622.5,
      "end": 623.1,
      "text": "Right away"
    },
    {
      "start": 623.1,
      "end": 623.7,
      "text": "Right away"
    },
    {
      "start": 623.7,
      "end": 624.6,
      "text": "to get you"
    },
    {
      "start": 624.6,
      "end": 625.48,
      "text": "because you're my daughter"
    },
    {
      "start": 625.48,
      "end": 625.84,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 625.84,
      "end": 627.0,
      "text": "And I didn't want to give you"
    },
    {
      "start": 627.0,
      "end": 627.66,
      "text": "up for adoption"
    },
    {
      "start": 627.66,
      "end": 628.82,
      "text": "오, 그럴 줄 알았는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 628.82,
      "end": 630.04,
      "text": "대답은?"
    },
    {
      "start": 630.44,
      "end": 631.48,
      "text": "29 days"
    },
    {
      "start": 631.48,
      "end": 632.02,
      "text": "이거였습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 632.02,
      "end": 633.08,
      "text": "29 days"
    },
    {
      "start": 633.08,
      "end": 633.84,
      "text": "오, surprise"
    },
    {
      "start": 633.84,
      "end": 635.24,
      "text": "오, 그러니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 635.24,
      "end": 636.88,
      "text": "왠지 좀 더 신중하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 636.88,
      "end": 637.66,
      "text": "또 신중하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 637.66,
      "end": 638.92,
      "text": "또 신중하기 위해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 638.92,
      "end": 640.38,
      "text": "이마만큼의 기간을"
    },
    {
      "start": 640.38,
      "end": 641.16,
      "text": "끈 게 아닌가"
    },
    {
      "start": 641.16,
      "end": 641.78,
      "text": "싶어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 641.78,
      "end": 643.6,
      "text": "Maybe her mom"
    },
    {
      "start": 643.6,
      "end": 644.5,
      "text": "was already gone"
    },
    {
      "start": 644.5,
      "end": 646.32,
      "text": "so he was really worried"
    },
    {
      "start": 646.32,
      "end": 647.54,
      "text": "Can I raise this girl"
    },
    {
      "start": 647.54,
      "end": 648.24,
      "text": "by myself?"
    },
    {
      "start": 648.36,
      "end": 648.88,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 648.88,
      "end": 650.18,
      "text": "He waited 29 days"
    },
    {
      "start": 650.18,
      "end": 651.7,
      "text": "29일 만에"
    },
    {
      "start": 651.7,
      "end": 652.54,
      "text": "그래도 다행히"
    },
    {
      "start": 652.54,
      "end": 653.8,
      "text": "그레이스를 찾아왔네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 653.8,
      "end": 654.78,
      "text": "네, 마지막으로"
    },
    {
      "start": 654.78,
      "end": 655.76,
      "text": "한 번 더 들어보겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 655.76,
      "end": 657.64,
      "text": "I hate fighting with you"
    },
    {
      "start": 657.64,
      "end": 659.22,
      "text": "You think you're ever"
    },
    {
      "start": 659.22,
      "end": 660.32,
      "text": "going to forgive me?"
    },
    {
      "start": 661.24,
      "end": 662.26,
      "text": "That's my other option"
    },
    {
      "start": 662.26,
      "end": 664.18,
      "text": "But I want to know everything"
    },
    {
      "start": 664.18,
      "end": 666.17,
      "text": "When you give a child"
    },
    {
      "start": 666.17,
      "end": 666.81,
      "text": "up for adoption"
    },
    {
      "start": 666.81,
      "end": 668.43,
      "text": "you've got 30 days"
    },
    {
      "start": 668.43,
      "end": 669.21,
      "text": "to change your mind"
    },
    {
      "start": 669.21,
      "end": 671.33,
      "text": "A grace period"
    },
    {
      "start": 671.33,
      "end": 672.62,
      "text": "How long did it"
    },
    {
      "start": 672.62,
      "end": 673.7,
      "text": "take you to decide"
    },
    {
      "start": 673.7,
      "end": 674.3,
      "text": "to come get me?"
    },
    {
      "start": 674.84,
      "end": 675.62,
      "text": "29 days"
    },
    {
      "start": 675.62,
      "end": 678.59,
      "text": "I like this conversation"
    },
    {
      "start": 678.59,
      "end": 680.77,
      "text": "It was a sincere conversation"
    },
    {
      "start": 680.77,
      "end": 681.51,
      "text": "Very sincere"
    },
    {
      "start": 681.51,
      "end": 682.15,
      "text": "Honest"
    },
    {
      "start": 682.15,
      "end": 683.55,
      "text": "It's a conversation"
    },
    {
      "start": 683.55,
      "end": 684.55,
      "text": "they needed to have"
    },
    {
      "start": 684.55,
      "end": 685.89,
      "text": "a little earlier in life"
    },
    {
      "start": 685.89,
      "end": 686.37,
      "text": "That's right"
    },
    {
      "start": 686.37,
      "end": 687.65,
      "text": "그랬으면 좋았을 텐데"
    },
    {
      "start": 687.65,
      "end": 689.09,
      "text": "At least they're having it now"
    },
    {
      "start": 689.09,
      "end": 690.31,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 690.31,
      "end": 691.49,
      "text": "지금이"
    },
    {
      "start": 691.49,
      "end": 692.51,
      "text": "그래도"
    },
    {
      "start": 692.51,
      "end": 693.39,
      "text": "주어졌을 때"
    },
    {
      "start": 693.39,
      "end": 694.49,
      "text": "시간이 주어졌을 때"
    },
    {
      "start": 694.49,
      "end": 695.53,
      "text": "이야기를 해주면"
    },
    {
      "start": 695.53,
      "end": 696.59,
      "text": "이렇게 오해가 풀립니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 696.59,
      "end": 699.51,
      "text": "네, 오늘 스크린 잉글리쉬는 여기까지고요"
    }
  ]
}